witch: 	0 dB, -10 dB<br />High Pass Filter: 	6 dB/octave @ 150 Hz <br />Equivalent noise: 	16 dB (A-weighted IEC 268-4)<br />S/N Ratio:	76 dB (Ref. 1 Pa A-weighted) <br />Max SPL for .5% THD:	130 dB/140 dB (0dB, -10 dB pad)<br />Power Requirements: 	48V Phantom Power (+/- 4V)<br />Size: 	55 x 195mm<br />Weight: 1.3 lbs/530g<br />Metal Finish: Black</p>\r\n<p><br /><strong>603 Specs</strong><br />Tube Type: Pressure gradient condenser microphone<br />Diaphragm:	6 micron gold-sputtered<br />Capsule Size:	22mm/.87 in.<br />Frequency Response:	30Hz - 20kHz <br />Polar pattern:	Cardioid<br />Sensitivity:	10mV/Pa<br />Output Impedance: 	200 ohms <br />Equivalent noise: 	18 dB (A-weighted IEC 268-4) <br />S/N Ratio:	76 dB (Ref. 1 Pa A-weighted) <br />Max SPL for .5% THD:	134 dB <br />Power Requirements: 	48V phantom power (+/-4V) <br />Size: 	22mm x 133mm/5.24 in. x 0.87 in.<br />Weight: 0.3 lbs/136.08g<br />Metal Finish: Silver</p>', 364.00, 'usd', true, 2, 0.00);",
