	112 dB (1 kHz and 1 Veff)<br />Тип амбюшура	circumaural<br />Длина кабеля, м	3<br />Гармонические искажения, %	&lt; 0,1 %<br />Вес, г	270</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<object width=\"560\" height=\"340\" data=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/SyVmLVnrRBs?fs=1&amp;hl=ru_RU&amp;color1=0x5d1719&amp;color2=0xcd311b\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\">\r\n<param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\" />\r\n<param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" />\r\n<param name=\"src\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/SyVmLVnrRBs?fs=1&amp;hl=ru_RU&amp;color1=0x5d1719&amp;color2=0xcd311b\" />\r\n<param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\" />\r\n</object>\r\n</p>', 183.00, 'eur', true, 2, 0.00);",
